data.description: ULTIMATE CHOICE HOME WARRANTY PROVIDED that will give you peice of mind as you settle in your new home!! Spacious 3 bed, 2 bath home finished with new LVP flooring in living area and master bedroom. Updated lighting and fixtures as well as detailed trim and moldings. French doors open to a spacious fenced in backyard with an accessory building finished out with window-unit air conditioning. Two-car garage leads into the mud-room landing. Both primary bedroom en-suite and additional full bath feature tub & shower combinations, with double vanity sinks in the primary. Follow your dream, home.
